                                                 ANGULAR

Basic Building Blocks


1) Module- to import 3rd party modules (root module -app.module.ts)
2) Component - to create html ts and css file

Basic Commands 
1) To create new project -- ng new project_name
2) TO create new Component-- ng g c component_name
3) To run angular file -- ng serve --open


baasic concepts
Data Binding----share data between components

ts-- component
html -- view

1)one way data Binding
data sharing only one direction
       1.1)component to view (ts->html)

          a)String interpolation-{{expression}}
          b)property Binding-[attribute_name]="property"

        1.2)view to components(html ton ts )
            a)event binding--(event_name)="function_name()"
            b)event bindimg using $event-($event_name)="function_name()"
            c)Event binding using tempelate referencing variable--#variable name





2)Two Way Databinding
Data sharing in both direction
